snippet.title: The Family Man S3 - Official Trailer | Raj & DK | Manoj Bajpayee, Jaideep Ahlawat | Prime Video IN
snippet.description:
Prime Video India Presents
The Family Man Season 3 Official Trailer 

SERIES:
"The Family Man," created by Raj & DK, an edgy and thrilling series on Prime Video, follows the life of Srikant Tiwari, a seemingly ordinary middle-class man who secretly works for the Threat Assessment and Surveillance Cell( TASC), a fictional cell of the National Investigation Agency in Mumbai. Balancing the demands of his high-stakes job and his family, life proves increasingly challenging as Srikant navigates dangerous missions against terrorists while trying to be a present husband and father. As he dives deeper into the murky world of espionage, Srikant must protect his loved ones from the perils of his covert profession, all while grappling with moral dilemmas that test his integrity and loyalty.

SEASON:
Outlawed and on the run, Srikant Tiwari faces sinister forces threatening to ignite chaos in Northeast India, uncovering a conspiracy that could plunge the nation into war.

Created by: Raj & DK

Directed by: Raj & DK, Suman Kumar, Tusshar Seyth
Produced by: Raj & DK
Written by Suman Kumar, Raj & DK
Screenplays by: Suman Kumar, Raj & DK, Sudhish Kamath, Nikhil Gonsalves  
Dialogues: Sumit Arora

Associate Producer: Anuradha Sharma

Associate Director: Chesta Goswami

Casting Director: Mukesh Chhabra CSA 

First Assistant Director: Durgesh Pratap Singh 
Additional Writing: Suhas Navarathna
Production Supervisor: Utkarsha Kohli 
Special Advisor: Bimal Parekh

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/PrimeVideoIN/
X: https://x.com/PrimeVideoIN

ABOUT PRIME VIDEO
Prime Video is a one-stop entertainment destination offering customers a vast collection of premium programming in one application available across several devices. On Prime Video, customers can find their favourite Indian and international original series, movies, TV shows, and more, across multiple languages ‚Äì including Indian-produced Original series like Mirzapur, Farzi, Panchayat, The Family Man, Dhootha, Jubilee, Dahaad, Made in Heaven, Suzhal ‚Äì The Vortex, Inspector Rishi, Poacher, Indian Police Force, Paatal Lok, Rainbow Rishta, Wedding.con; Original movies like Maja Ma, Ammu, Mast Mein Rehne Ka; popular global Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Fallout, Reacher, The Boys, The Wheel of Time, Road House, The Idea of You; some of the biggest post-theatrical films; direct-to-service films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Bawaal, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, Pippa, HOME, Sharmajee Ki Beti, and many more of such titles. Additionally, Prime Video‚Äôs video entertainment marketplace, offers customers programming from partners such as Lionsgate Play, Discovery+ Crunchyroll, BBC Player, Sony Pictures ‚Äì Stream, MGM+, FanCode, Chaupal, Manorama Max, Eros Now, Hoichoi, Anime Times, to name a few, via Prime Video add-on-subscriptions, as well as the option to rent movies, regardless of whether customers have a Prime membership or not. Customers can also go behind the scenes of their favorite movies and series with exclusive X-Ray access. Prime Video is one benefit among many that provides savings, convenience, and entertainment as part of the Prime membership. For more info visit www.amazon.com/primevideo.

en.description:
Prime Video India Presents
The Family Man Season 3 Official Trailer 

SERIES:
"The Family Man," created by Raj & DK, an edgy and thrilling series on Prime Video, follows the life of Srikant Tiwari, a seemingly ordinary middle-class man who secretly works for the Threat Assessment and Surveillance Cell( TASC), a fictional cell of the National Investigation Agency in Mumbai. Balancing the demands of his high-stakes job and his family, life proves increasingly challenging as Srikant navigates dangerous missions against terrorists while trying to be a present husband and father. As he dives deeper into the murky world of espionage, Srikant must protect his loved ones from the perils of his covert profession, all while grappling with moral dilemmas that test his integrity and loyalty.

SEASON:
Outlawed and on the run, Srikant Tiwari faces sinister forces threatening to ignite chaos in Northeast India, uncovering a conspiracy that could plunge the nation into war.

snippet.title: Dil Kya Kare Jab Kisi Ko (Lyric Video) - Julie | Kishore Kumar
snippet.description:
‚ÄúDil Kya Kare Jab Kisi Ko‚Äù is one of the most soulful romantic songs from the 1975 film Julie. Sung in the golden voice of Kishore Kumar, the music is composed by the legendary Rajesh Roshan, with heartfelt lyrics penned by Anand Bakshi. This evergreen melody beautifully captures the emotions of love and longing, making it one of the most cherished classics of Hindi cinema. 

Credits: 
Singer: Kishore Kumar
Music: Rajesh Roshan
Lyrics: Anand Bakshi
Label: Universal Music India

Lyrics: 

 Dil kya kare jab kisi se 
 Kisi ko pyar ho jaaye 
 Jaane kahan kab kisi ko 
 Kisi se pyar ho jaaye 
 Oonchi-oonchi diwaaron si 
 Is duniya ki rasmein 
 Ho na kuch tere bas mein Julie 
 Na kuch mere bas mein 
 Dil kya kare jab kisi se 
 Kisi ko pyar ho jaaye 
 Jaane kahan kab kisi ko 
 Kisi se pyar ho jaaye 

Jaise parwat pe ghata jhukti hai 
 Jaise saagar se lehar uthti hai 
 Aise kisi chehre pe nigaah rukti hai 
 Jaise parwat pe ghata jhukti hai 
 Jaise saagar se lehar uthti hai 
 Aise kisi chehre pe nigaah rukti hai 
 Ho rok nahin sakti nazron ko 
 Duniya bhar ki rasmein 
 Na kuch tere bas mein Julie 
 Na kuch mere bas mein 
 Dil kya kare jab kisi se 
 Kisi ko pyar ho jaaye 
 Jaane kahan kab kisi ko 
 Kisi se pyar ho jaaye 

 Aa main teri yaad mein sab ko bhula doon 
 Duniya ko teri tasveer bana doon 
 Mera bas chale to dil cheer ke dikha doon 
 Aa main teri yaad mein sab ko bhula doon 
 Duniya ko teri tasveer bana doon 
 Mera bas chale to dil cheer ke dikha doon 
 Ho daud raha hai sath lahu ke 
 Pyar tera nas-nas mein 
 Na kuch tere bas mein Julie 
 Na kuch mere bas mein 

 Dil kya kare jab kisi se 
 Kisi ko pyar ho jaaye 
 Jaane kahan kab kisi ko 
 Kisi se pyar ho jaaye 
 Oonchi-oonchi diwaaron si 
 Is duniya ki rasmein 
 Ho na kuch tere bas mein Julie 
 Na kuch mere bas mein 
 Dil kya kare jab kisi se 
 Kisi ko pyar ho jaaye 
 Jaane kahan kab kisi ko 
 Kisi se pyar ho jaaye

snippet.title: Man Vs Baby | Official Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
After a job looking after a high-tech mansion ended in disaster thanks to an irritating insect in Man vs Bee, Trevor Bingley (Rowan Atkinson) has left the stressful world of housesitting for the quieter life of a school caretaker. That is, until a lucrative offer to look after a luxury London penthouse over Christmas proves too tempting to resist. But on the last day of term, when no one comes to collect the Baby Jesus from the school nativity, Trevor finds himself with another undersized and very unexpected companion. With a penthouse to protect and a baby to burp, will Trevor be able to have the calm Christmas he hopes for, or will festivities descend into chaos?

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81516058

snippet.title: Matter (Official Music Video) - Sumit Parta & Panther | New Haryanvi Song 2025
snippet.description:
Presenting new Haryanvi hip hop 2025 ‚Äì Matter by Sumit Parta & Panther

Bringing you the raw and fearless vibe of Haryana with "Matter", the latest fire track by Sumit Parta & Panther.
This song defines real street energy ‚Äî filled with power, attitude, and pride. With intense lyrics, bold delivery, and unstoppable flow, Matter is all about dominance, loyalty, and living with no compromise.

If you believe in your hustle and never back down ‚Äî this one‚Äôs for you. 

Song Credits: 
Song Title: Matter
Singer: Sumit Parta & Panther
Music: Xtacy
Lyricist/Composer: Sumit Parta & Panther

Director: Mohan BeTaab
DOP: Nishan Singh

Distribution By: EYP Consulting
Distribution & Marketing Partner: EYP Creations & Warner Music India
Digitally Managed By: Prince Pannu

Lyrics:
Gaadi Uchi Uchi Rakhe Chale Talke Sedan 
Baat Lambi Koni Khiche Khde Pair Samadhan 
Sath Khaadi Panchgami Kon Gunda Paake Shayami 
Mkha Itni Re Bdi Koni Kise Ki Dukan 

Yaari Dosti Me Sara Ghar Phuk Dewa 
Par Yaari Dosti Me Koni Roli Chalya Kre 
Jiki Nasa Me Se Pani Woye Kre Samjhota 
 Mhare Matter  Me Sun Sidhi Goli Chalya  Kre 

Bair Mhare Chori Sun Dada Layi Chalre H
Gelya Chacha Tau Aale Mere Bhai Chalre H 
Kayi Sale Mere Laan Ki Sakeem Sochre H 
Anty Party Te  Krn Collab Pochre H 

Phle Karam Kand Krya Ib Bnya Hu Me  Singer 
Choro Jaata Ko  Sage Bishnoiya Ka Tinger 
Adhe Shise Khule Bhar Kade Rakhe Chora Finger
5,7 Bhai Paad Dewa Karwayi 
Konya Krke Yo Chora Kathi Toli Chalya Krya 
Jiki Nasa Me Se Pani Woye Kre Samjhota 
Mhare Matter  Me Sun Sidhi Goli Chalya Kre 

Ye Ghoda Chalta Bhi Aur Jalta Bhi
Bas Bhaagta Bhagataa Lekin Peecha Hat-ta Nahi
Ye Ghoda Jeet Dilata Aur Karta Barbaadi
Deta Nahi Maafi Hai Karta Sardari
Aur Faadein Beech Se Gar Bane Koi Jyada Patwari

Raub Jamata Ye Gaddafi Nahi Jhukta Bhale Hi Katta Sir
Mujhe Gaddari Dikhe Minute Se Pehle Got The Vision Of Gandhari
Hoti Mahabharat Tune Buri Nazar Se Dekh Li Gar Meri Panchali
Tere Chacha Bappa Sabki Karwadu Baikunth Tayyari
Aur Sun
Kam Se Jyaada Hai Zubaan Ki Izzat
Aukat Se Jyaada Karte Iman Ki Izzat
Chadhai Se Jyaada Ache Insan Ki
Hum Bhaukal Se Zyaada Karte Ache Khandan Ki Izzat
Gunday Badmash Company Me Jaise Ye Yashraj Ki Picture
Pakke Usool, Lathi Hai Har Sanp Ki Ksimat
Naseeb Me Bheji Bhagwan Ne Pehli Ashiqui Likh Kar
Aur Duji Maut Seene Pe Goli Hath Me Pistol

Hoti Pitayi Lage Kohli Mara Kare
Judge Sab Bole Galat Karam Pe Tere Moti Dhara Lage
Khatey Bikaneri Na Goli Guli Khaya Kare
Panther Bhaiya Jaha Phonchey Og Og Nara Lage

Mkha Kaan Khol Dhyan Te Tu Baat Sun Chooti 
Badmasha Ki Re Koi Prem Khani Konya Hoti 
Tane Mare Subha Shyam Fer  Bole Ga Re Gaam 
Gundya Gelya Link H Flane Ki H Poti 
Karke Ne Kand Kde Bhaje Koni Yaar 
Mhari Sadka Pe Gadi Ye Slowly Chalya Kre 

Jiki Nasa Me Se Pani Woye Kre Samjhota 
Mhare Matter  Me Sun Sidhi Goli Chalya Kre



Stay Tuned & Subscribe/Follow me on:
* Youtube: https://www.youtube.com/c/SumitParta
* Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/sumitparta09/

snippet.title: Michael | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
MICHAEL - in cinemas soon.
____ 
Michael is the cinematic portrayal of the life and legacy of one of the most influential artists the world has ever known.
 
The film tells the story of Michael Jackson‚Äôs life beyond the music, tracing his journey from the discovery of his extraordinary talent as the lead of the Jackson Five, to the visionary artist whose creative ambition fueled a relentless pursuit to become the biggest entertainer in the world.
 
Highlighting both his life off-stage and some of the most iconic performances from his early solo career, the film gives audiences a front-row seat to Michael Jackson as never before. This is where his story begins.
 
Michael stars Jaafar Jackson in his feature film debut, Nia Long (Empire, The Best Man franchise), Laura Harrier (BlacKkKlansman, Spider-Man: Homecoming) and Juliano Krue Valdi (The Loud House, Arco), with Miles Teller (Top Gun: Maverick, Whiplash) and two-time Academy Award¬Æ nominee Colman Domingo (Sing Sing, Rustin).
 
Directed by Antoine Fuqua, the award-winning filmmaker of Training Day, Olympus Has Fallen and The Equalizer franchise, from a screenplay by three-time Academy Award¬Æ nominee John Logan (Gladiator, The Aviator), the film is produced by Academy Award¬Æ winner Graham King (The Departed, Bohemian Rhapsody), John Branca (executive producer This Is It, Thriller 40) and John McClain (executive producer This Is It, Michael Jackson Live at Wembley July 16, 1988).

Highlighting both his life off-stage and some of the most iconic performances from his early solo career, the film gives audiences a front-row seat to Michael Jackson as never before. This is where his story begins.
 
Michael stars Jaafar Jackson in his feature film debut, Nia Long (Empire, The Best Man franchise), Laura Harrier (BlacKkKlansman, Spider-Man: Homecoming) and Juliano Krue Valdi (The Loud House, Arco), with Miles Teller (Top Gun: Maverick, Whiplash) and two-time Academy Award¬Æ nominee Colman Domingo (Sing Sing, Rustin).
 
Directed by Antoine Fuqua, the award-winning filmmaker of Training Day, Olympus Has Fallen and The Equalizer franchise, from a screenplay by three-time Academy Award¬Æ nominee John Logan (Gladiator, The Aviator), the film is produced by Academy Award¬Æ winner Graham King (The Departed, Bohemian Rhapsody), John Branca (executive producer This Is It, Thriller 40) and John McClain (executive producer This Is It, Michael Jackson Live at Wembley July 16, 1988).

snippet.title: NZ vs WI | 3rd T20I | Highlights | West Indies Tour Of New Zealand 2025
snippet.description:
New Zealand won the third T20I against the West Indies by 9 runs in a match played on November 9, 2025, at Saxton Oval in Nelson. The victory gives New Zealand a 2-1 lead in the five-match series. New Zealand batted first and posted a total of 177 for 9. West Indies made a strong late comeback but fell short of the target in the final over, scoring 168 runs.

snippet.title: Pritam, KK - Mat Aazma Re
snippet.description:
Pritam, KK - Mat Aazma Re
Stream/Download ~ https://open.spotify.com/track/0mh4VutnDyBn1sqcp05MZD?si=b5ec48693580447d

~ MUSIC INFO ~

Lyrics ~ Pritam, KK - Mat Aazma Re

Mat aazma re, phir se bula re
Apna bana le, hoon beqaraar
Tujhko hi chaaha dil hai ye karta
Haan, betahaasha tujhse hi pyaar
Hasratein baar-baar, baar-baar yaar ki karo
Khwahishein baar-baar, baar-baar yaar ki karo
Chaahatein baar-baar, baar-baar yaar ki karo
Mannatein baar-baar, baar-baar yaar ki karo
Hum zaar-zaar rote hain, khud se khafa bhi hote hain
Hum ye pehle kyun na samjhe? Tum faqat mere
Dil ka qaraar khote hain, kahan chain se bhi sote hain
Humne dil mein kyun bichhaaye shak ye gehre?
Hasratein baar-baar, baar-baar yaar ki karo
Khwahishein baar-baar, baar-baar yaar ki karo
Chaahatein baar-baar, baar-baar yaar ki karo
Mannatein baar-baar, baar-baar yaar ki karo
Tere hi khwaab dekhna, teri hi raah taakna
Tere hi vaaste hai meri har wafa
Teri hi baat sochna, teri hi yaad odhna
Tere hi vaaste hai meri har dua
Tera hi saath maangna, teri hi baanh thaamna
Mujhe jaana nahi kahin tere bina
Tu mujhse phir na roothna, kabhi kahin na chhootna
Mera koi nahi yahan tere siva
Hasratein baar-baar, baar-baar yaar ki karo
Khwahishein baar-baar, baar-baar yaar ki karo
Chaahatein baar-baar, baar-baar yaar ki karo
Mannatein baar-baar, baar-baar yaar ki karo

Lara Lappa Lara Lappa Lai Rakhdi...üî•
Presenting Kokaina 8K video, sung and written by Badshah & Simiran Kaur Dhadli, with beats by Hiten, this track is bold, raw, and unforgettable.

üëâ Subscribe to Saregama Music: https://bit.ly/3FkAS0W

Credits:
Song: Kokaina
Singers & Lyricist: Badshah, Simiran Kaur Dhadli
Music Director: Hiten
Mix Master: Hiten
Sarangi: Momin Khan
Featuring Starcast: Badshah, Simiran Kaur Dhadli, Natasha Bharadwaj

Lyrics:
Kokaina
Tu hai bandi ghalat
De kaya palat
mohol badalati hai kaise

Buri aafat tu
Buri aadat tu
Mujhe hit karti hai jaise

Kokaina ina ina ina ina ina ina (mujhe hit karti hai jaise)
Kokaina ina ina ina ina ina ina (mujhe hit karti hai jaise)

Kokaina ina ina ina ina ina ina (mujhe hit karti hai jaise)
Kokaina ina ina ina ina ina ina

Yeh pareshan karegi 
Leke jaan rahegi
Bada nuksaan karegi
Aaj koi kaand karegi

Tu hi hai alpha tu hi hai beta
Galt jo dekhe tujhe
Tujhe tod du gita 
saanvle rang ki nagin jaisi
Hit karti hai jaise chitta

Aaju baaju na koi fatakra 
Launda koi na palk jhapakra
Tar tar tar hai Paseena tapakra
Vo bhi ni hatri mai bhi ni hatra 

Tak tak tina
Sun o Haseena
Kamar ghuma
aane de paseena
Aapka scene me tod na koi
game me apna bhi tod koi na

Kokaina ina ina ina ina ina ina (mujhe hit karti hai jaise)
Kokaina ina ina ina ina ina ina (mujhe hit karti hai jaise)

Kokaina ina ina ina ina ina ina (mujhe hit karti hai jaise)
Kokaina ina ina ina ina ina ina

Lara Lappa Lara Lappa Lai Rakhdi..
Tere Varge Main Jeba Vich Pai Rakhdi..
Jo Tu Khede Gemman Ehna Di Main Coach Rahi Aan..
Ve Ki Motive Ae Tera 
Hale Soch Rahi Aan..
Mere Nal Behnde Jehde Sare Bande Main..
Jiddan Jatti Hit Kre ,,Kiddan Kar Lau Cocaine..
Jado Boldi Main, Bullan Cho Barood Girda..
Mainu Janda Zamana ,,Mera Style Insane..

Tere Jise bde Haandey mere Paacche Chhore..
Janaaban Ke b Darshan Mehnge Horey..
Jehdi Akh Ne V Jatti Takki Khumb Vargi..
Oo Akh Fir Mud K Soi Na..

Kokaina ina ina ina ina ina ina (mujhe hit karti hai jaise)
Kokaina ina ina ina ina ina ina (mujhe hit karti hai jaise)

Kokaina ina ina ina ina ina ina (mujhe hit karti hai jaise)
Kokaina ina ina ina ina ina ina
(Mujhe hit karti hai jaise)

snippet.description:
Presenting the Video song of 'Nallaru po' from 'Dude', Written & Directed by Keerthiswaran featuring Pradeep Ranganathan, Mamitha Baiju, R.Sarath Kumar, Hridhu Haroon,Rohini, Aishwarya sharma, Dravid selvam & Others.

An @SaiAbhyankkar  Musical 
Song Title: 'Nallaru po'
Album: Dude

Music Credits:

Composed and produced by @SaiAbhyankkar 
Singers: Tipu , @SaiAbhyankkar , Mohit Chauhan
Lyricist : Vivek 
Synth ,keys and Bass programmed by @SaiAbhyankkar

Violin - Chinmayi

Lyrics:

Nee ketaa unna kooda un kaiyil vittu poguren
Aasa pola vaazhndhukkoyen po
Un mela kaadhal vachene
Thothadhaalum theerala
Ponadhaalum maarala 

Nee ketaa unna kooda un kaiyil vittu poguren
Aasa pola vaazhndhukko di po
Ennalum Kaadhal kuthadhu 
Parvayal Yenga Vechaale 

Paakaama pesaama seraama ponaalum 
Ennaalum nallaru po 
Hey thaangaama thoongaama naan inga vaazhndhaalum
Neeyaachum nallaaru po
 
Kaadhalaa en nenjam
Yekkamaa aanan naane
Kaayamaa nee senjum
Sirikkirene
Yaaradi kutham solla 
En vidhi  enna kolla 
Nee vantha nenjukkulla  
Ippothu onnumilla 

Veroru kayyoda un veral paathen naane 
Vegura nenjoda pogurene
Nethu un kannil naane
Innaikku yaaro dhaane 
Thindaadurene maane
Thaa po nu vittutene 

Paakaama pesaama enkuda seraama ponaalum nallaru po 
Hey thaangaama thoongaama naan inga vaazhndhaalum 
Neeyaachum nallaarupo 

Hey Innoruthanoda nee poga 
Ullolachaloda naan poga 
Enna panna poren Thikku theriyaadhe 
Aanaa neeyum po
 
Hey Ennapanna poren kekaadha
Indha pakkam neeyum paakaadha
Michamulla kaadhal atchadhaya podum 
Nallaa vaazhu po

snippet.description:
Song one from the iconic Tamil devotional album Kattum Katti ‚Äì Sannathiyil Kattum Katti narrates the divine journey of a group of Ayyappa devotees. The song follows their spiritual path from receiving the Tulasi mala from the Guruswami, practicing Mandal Viratham, preparing Irumudi, and traveling through Erumeli, Periya Paathai, Pamba, and finally reaching Sannidhanam.

This evergreen classic is one of the biggest Tamil Ayyappan devotional hits by Srihari, loved across generations. With melodious tunes, emotional depth, devotional energy, and spiritual storytelling, Srihari‚Äôs Ayyappan songs have created a unique musical style in Tamil bhakti music.

The album features compositions by the legendary Aravind, known for devotional hits like Ayiram Kannudaiyal, Kallum Mullum Kaalukku Metthai, Mundhi Mundhi Vinayagane, and the popular Namashivaya Om Namashivaya (SPB). Lyrics are penned by Dr. Kiruthiya, also known for Onbathu Kolum Ondrai Kana.

Other popular Srihari Ayyappan albums:
Ayyappana Padu, Ayyappanai Thedi, Ayyappan Utsavam, Irumudi Thangi, Mandala Poojai, Mandala Viratham

localized.description:
Song one from the iconic Tamil devotional album Kattum Katti ‚Äì Sannathiyil Kattum Katti narrates the divine journey of a group of Ayyappa devotees. The song follows their spiritual path from receiving the Tulasi mala from the Guruswami, practicing Mandal Viratham, preparing Irumudi, and traveling through Erumeli, Periya Paathai, Pamba, and finally reaching Sannidhanam.

This evergreen classic is one of the biggest Tamil Ayyappan devotional hits by Srihari, loved across generations. With melodious tunes, emotional depth, devotional energy, and spiritual storytelling, Srihari‚Äôs Ayyappan songs have created a unique musical style in Tamil bhakti music.

The album features compositions by the legendary Aravind, known for devotional hits like Ayiram Kannudaiyal, Kallum Mullum Kaalukku Metthai, Mundhi Mundhi Vinayagane, and the popular Namashivaya Om Namashivaya (SPB). Lyrics are penned by Dr. Kiruthiya, also known for Onbathu Kolum Ondrai Kana.

Other popular Srihari Ayyappan albums:
Ayyappana Padu, Ayyappanai Thedi, Ayyappan Utsavam, Irumudi Thangi, Mandala Poojai, Mandala Viratham
